description: Ultra-rare 2-bed plus study with garage parking at the popular Court Square Press building — this brick-and-beam residence offers the perfect blend of historic character and modern updates. Oversized windows overlook a tranquil bamboo courtyard, filling the home with natural light. At the heart of the home, a generous open-concept living space is framed by two spacious bedrooms, each offering en-suite baths and walk-in closets. The second bedroom includes a unique bonus area, formerly an elevator shaft, perfect for a home office, creative studio, or expanded walk-in closet. The kitchen is appointed with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Amenities include 24/7 concierge, garage parking, a pool terrace with grills and Wi-Fi, fitness center, screening room with catering kitchen, and more. Ideally located near top restaurants, shops, the Red Line, major highways, and Logan Airport.
